:{{DIcon|Talk}} The Ambrosial Arbor Crisis has blown up big time...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000129: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act90000129.json-->
::The Ambrosial Arbor Crisis has blown up big time...
::'''Mengming:''' Totally. Before the Ambrosial Arbor's growth happened, I had been thinking about my parents, who always told me to turn a crisis into an opportunity. Since the Ambrosial Arbor's new growth was a crisis, I thought I would be able to turn it into an opportunity.
::'''Mengming:''' If I succeeded, it could be a great boost to my tea house's business. So I went to Mr. Xiyan to discuss it.
::'''Mengming:''' In the end, Mr. Xiyan told me off and said that I shouldn't have thought of profiting from the crisis...
::'''Mengming:''' And the crisis ended in the blink of an eye before I could come up with a plan to make use of it. *sigh* Things are ever-changing in this world, and it teaches us to be adaptive to changes. Running a business is tough, and I still have a long way to go.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
